      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3239,
        3320
      ],
      "content": "Upon first use of Hudson, complete the initial setup at <ph id=\"ph1\">`http://localhost:8080/`</ph>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3330,
        3573
      ],
      "content": "After you complete the initial setup, cancel the running instance of the Hudson WAR, start the Hudson WAR again, and  re-open the Hudson dashboard, <ph id=\"ph1\">`http://localhost:8080/`</ph>, which you will use to install and configure the Azure Storage plugin."
    },
    {
      "content": "While a typical Hudson CI solution would be set up to run as a service, running the Hudson war at the command line will be sufficient for this tutorial.",
      "pos": [
        3583,
        3735
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "An Azure account.",
      "pos": [
        3739,
        3756
      ]
    },
    {
