      ],
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Post-build Actions<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> section of the job configuration, click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Upload artifacts to Microsoft Azure Blob storage<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        6748,
        6812
      ],
      "content": "For <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Storage Account Name<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, select the storage account to use."
