    },
    {
      "content": "In the Hudson dashboard, click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Build Now<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> to run <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>MyJob<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>.",
