    },
    {
      "content": "Container names and blob names are lowercase (and case-sensitive) in Azure storage.",
      "pos": [
        8962,
        9045
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Within the list of blobs for the container named <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>myjob<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> you should see <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>hello.txt<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> and <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>date.txt<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        9046,
        9151
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Copy the URL for either of these items and open it in your browser.",
      "pos": [
