    {
      "pos": [
        10638,
        10702
      ],
      "content": "For <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Storage account name<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, select the storage account to use."
    },
    {
      "content": "For <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Container name<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, specify the name of the container that has the blobs you want to download.",
      "pos": [
        10706,
        10804
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can use environment variables.",
      "pos": [
        10805,
        10839
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Blob name<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, specify the blob name.",
      "pos": [
        10843,
        10884
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can use environment variables.",
      "pos": [
        10885,
        10919
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Also, you can use an asterisk, as a wildcard after you specify the initial letter(s) of the blob name.",
      "pos": [
