      "pos": [
        11023,
        11109
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "[Optional] For <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Download path<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, specify the path on the Hudson machine where you want to download files from Azure blob storage.",
      "pos": [
        11113,
        11243
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Environment variables can also be used.",
